---
title: Speedy Creamy Chorizo & Sweetcorn Pasta with Spinach
description: You can’t beat creamy, cheesy pasta, and that’s exactly what this recipe delivers. The smooth, creamy taste of the pasta sauce made with creme fraiche compliments the stronger flavours of smoky chorizo, charred sweetcorn and garlic. Spinach is stirred through the pasta for a slight bitterness that works perfectly with the creaminess and an extra dose of veggies. With a total cooking time of 20 minutes, this dish is minimal effort and maximum flavour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-chorizo-sweetcorn-pasta-60ccdf8a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/creamy-chorizo-sweetcorn-pasta-5d289d41a987840009733e70-414dacdf.pdf
